{"tid":1458373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［非割席］要捉哂今日蒲頭既連登網絡卧底！","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:15:38.000Z","uid":18638,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"79b8e7fad2ac8ef6db35670d1094008ffa03279d","tid":1458373,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"政府根本無預過因為尋日既事會引致咁多人突襲機場<br />\n所以佢地係無準備既情況下加上機場有好多限制令佢地用唔到室外既清場方法<br />\n就惟有動員左大量網絡卧底去帶風向 但同時都令佢地呢批account浮左面<br />\n<br />\n我建議連仔一定要捉哂呢班浮左面既卧底出黎防止佢地再帶風向<br />\n雖然有機會誤中副車 但佢地可控制既非P牌連登會員一定有限 所以今次係大好機會去削弱佢地日後放流料既機會 <br />\n雖然連仔已經限制P牌一日只可以開一post, 但佢擁有既P牌AC一定比普通會員多<br />\n所以希望連仔可以考慮全面禁止P牌仔開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾隻鬼例子：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1456156/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1456156/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1456108/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1456108/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1455649/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1455649/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bbf126203f9d3fa9996cdbb8e87a39b71d54a1b2","tid":1458373,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:55:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9e0e4e78a6d0a52656da40b689e894442e13f508","tid":1458373,"uid":19287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"Dklm熄燈都夠膽講，當現場d人on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33849a381037428a75c4d3ff1a6a87162768e94","tid":1458373,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e7c99f5af637e2b0b24edaed6678f2fbff6d4f49","tid":1458373,"uid":157862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"現場人表示絕對認同呀，連仔一定要bam死呢啲account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo